summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5662 for the improvement of A portion of The Alley in Block 49, Yesler's 2nd Addition, being the portion of the alley between 24th Avenue North and 25th Avenue North, from East Madison Street to East Thomas Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 74896, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
